{"idCodigoAcceso":"D7963A39","nroRegistro":"RS-16-2026","caratula":"MELENDEZ POLLI FLORENCIO JOSE CRUZ C/ CASTRO CARLOS EDGARDO S/MATERIA A CATEGORIZAR","indice":"otros","subindice":"otro","demandante":"MELENDEZ POLLI FLORENCIO JOSE CRUZ","demandado":"CASTRO CARLOS EDGARDO","tipoCausa":"MATERIA A CATEGORIZAR","quePaso":"En caso afirmativo ¿cuándo ingresó, cómo se componía su jornada laboral, a cuánto ascendían sus haberes?","resultadoCausa":"No determinado","hechosExplicacion":"En caso afirmativo ¿cuándo ingresó, cómo se componía su jornada laboral, a cuánto ascendían sus haberes?","decision":"Sentencia que prescribe el artículo 44 inciso \"e\" de la ley 11.653, en la causa caratulada “Meléndez Polli Florencio José Cruz c/ Castro Carlos Edgardo s/ materia a categorizar”, Expediente N°37.850 ANTECEDENTES A fs. 23/41 se presenta mediante representación letrada, Florencio José Cruz Melendez Polli, incoando formal demanda contra Carlos Edgardo Castro, de quienes reclama las indemnizaciones legales por despido. A tal fin informa su fecha de ingreso a prestar tareas como vigilancia y seguridad en el resto-bar “Mr. Johnes”, propiedad del demandado, su jornada de trabajo y haberes percibidos. Señala que la relación nunca fue registrada y que ante una negativa de tareas se inició el tráfico postal entre ambos, que culminó con su decisión de darse por despedido. Plantea la inconstitucionalidad de las leyes 23.928, 25.561 y 214/02; practica liquidación; ofrece prueba y, finalmente, hace reserva del caso federal. Ordenado el traslado que manda el artículo 28 de la ley 11.653, a fs. 49/53 se presenta Carlos Edgardo Castro, por intermedio de su letrado patrocinante, quien opone excepción de falta de legitimación pasiva; niega puntualmente las afirmaciones contenidas en la demanda; brinda su versión de los hechos y, por último, propone prueba. Dispuesto el traslado que prescribe el artículo 29 de la ley 11.653, la parte actora no cumple con dicha carga procesal. A fs. 75/76 se dicta...","embedding":[0.08160638064146042,0.053174782544374466,-0.04336679354310036,-0.03429192304611206,-0.03542323037981987,-0.007433975115418434,0.014268983155488968,0.03425007686018944,0.012353122234344482,-0.00485978601500392,0.03303736448287964,0.029032764956355095,-0.06114371865987778,-0.025649460032582283,-0.018171438947319984,-0.019613677635788918,-0.04116404429078102,-0.06304508447647095,-0.06338062882423401,-0.010209867730736732,-0.026962295174598694,-0.06253397464752197,-0.024578338488936424,-0.053437475115060806,0.16588766872882843,-0.007151567377150059,-0.012524435296654701,-0.006182751152664423,-0.028605373576283455,-0.025050383061170578,-0.05726620554924011,-0.0192111823707819,0.025465115904808044,-0.01862112618982792,-0.0005830388981848955,0.036704838275909424,0.08278324455022812,0.021251125261187553,0.0483190156519413,0.07332301139831543,-0.004172512795776129,-0.08055528253316879,-0.01992913894355297,0.054589077830314636,0.007383938878774643,0.02382505312561989,0.03287513926625252,-0.03742027282714844,-0.08211807906627655,-0.016794567927718163,0.050088491290807724,0.014168327674269676,0.04330964386463165,0.010949085466563702,-0.01387283205986023,0.023446472361683846,0.03498813509941101,-0.037127621471881866,-0.03446615859866142,0.05323471128940582,-0.09800485521554947,0.03090386837720871,-0.09890870749950409,-0.0005030089523643255,0.012821385636925697,-0.03830718994140625,-0.014361835084855556,-0.06910654157400131,-0.048707008361816406,0.031335677951574326,0.008556929416954517,-0.0566602498292923,-0.03669258579611778,-0.03452891483902931,0.0037363297306001186,0.006501680705696344,0.023193685337901115,0.06494715809822083,-0.015613989904522896,-0.03677937760949135,0.0337044894695282,-0.014586186967790127,-0.06409165263175964,0.04813298583030701,-0.032391536980867386,-0.018368583172559738,-0.05021391808986664,0.02211109921336174,0.050629232078790665,-0.011452043429017067,0.0030161007307469845,-0.07136546075344086,-0.0154891237616539,-0.03261860087513923